This aligns with classic ultimatum game theory, where proposers maximize their payoff when responders have no leverage. Since BLUE cannot retaliate or demand more, the dominant strategy is to extract the maximum possible value while ensuring the deal is accepted. Offering 1 Dollar achieves this perfectly.
